ganization, and individuals tend to be loyal to a given area rather than a roost.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Garg, Kritika M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chattopadhyay, Balaji", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ramakrishnan, Uma", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/c56470493c95c44b39478873be50e9c5", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/5ff8dc161eee55b8bcec6898bcffbef51ef329a3fbcd818ef00d06bd8fd4ac25", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/BRQQCQWM", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/BRQQCQWM", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/819cebe73f6746be00cacb808b625d21!/b221066-223523", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "2", "pages": "172024", "title": "Royal Society Open Science", "volume": "5"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/c56470493c95c44b39478873be50e9c5"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:BRQQCQWM"}, {"identifier": "10.1098/rsos.172024"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13487787"}}]}}, "title": "Social structure of the harem-forming promiscuous frui